                    <p><em><strong>                    <strong><em> Transitions: </em></strong></strong><em> Not infrequently, consortia tend to be transitory efforts, for a variety of reasons. Sometimes initiatives fail, sometimes they overlap, and sometimes they just finish what they were formed to accomplish. The following is an example of one such transition.</em> </em></p></td>
